Supplementary Terms

The following supplementary terms apply in addition to the CC BY-NC-SA 4.0
license above. These terms are set by the copyright holder and apply to all
files in this repository unless otherwise noted.

1. Microsoft Employee Exception

   Employees of Microsoft Corporation are granted permission to use, modify,
   and distribute the contents of this repository for internal and commercial
   purposes within the scope of their employment at Microsoft, provided that
   appropriate attribution is given.

2. Prohibition of AI/ML Training Use

   The contents of this repository shall NOT be used, in whole or in part, as
   training data, fine-tuning data, or evaluation data for any artificial
   intelligence (AI) or machine learning (ML) model, including but not limited
   to large language models (LLMs), without explicit written permission from
   the copyright holder.

3. Prohibition of Collection/Aggregation Redistribution

   The contents of this repository shall NOT be included, in whole or in part,
   in any collection, aggregation, compilation, or "awesome list" repository
   for the purpose of redistribution or public re-hosting. Linking to this
   repository (via URL) is permitted and encouraged.

4. Attribution Format

   When providing attribution, please use the following format:

   yamapan (@aktsmm) - https://github.com/aktsmm

